<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Earth%27s_horizon_as_seen_from_Shuttle_Endeavour.jpg" class="image" title="View of Earth's horizon as seen from Space Shuttle Endeavour, 2002."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Earth%27s_horizon_as_seen_from_Shuttle_Endeavour.jpg/250px-Earth%27s_horizon_as_seen_from_Shuttle_Endeavour.jpg" width="250" height="165" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Earth%27s_horizon_as_seen_from_Shuttle_Endeavour.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
